Definition: deciduous or semi-evergreen tree having scented sepia to yellow flowers in drooping racemes and pods whose pulp is used medicinally
Example: tropical Asia and Central and South America and Australia
Synonyms: drumstick_tree, purging_cassia, pudding_pipe_tree, canafistola, canafistula, Cassia_fistula, cassia, deciduous, or, semi-evergreen, tree, having, scented, sepia, to, yellow, flowers, in, drooping, racemes, and, pods, whose, pulp, is, used, medicinally, tropical, Asia, Central, South, America, Australia
Category: noun.plant
